Command> array=(aaa bbb1 ccc aaa1 bbb2 aaa33); echo ${array[(i)bbb*]}     # -> 2

Keywords>
        > zsh
        > search

TL;DR> bbbで始まる最初の要素のインデックスを取得

Example01> array=(aaa bbb1 ccc aaa1 bbb2 aaa33); echo ${array[(i)xxx*]}     # -> 7
Example02> array=(aaa bbb1 ccc aaa1 bbb2 aaa33); echo ${array[(I)bbb*]}     # -> 5   # 逆順

Reference> https://qiita.com/mollifier/items/f897b3fddd2d10369333
